\frac{x^n-(-\alpha)^n}{x-(-\alpha)}=x^{n-1}\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\frac{(-a)^k}{x^k}
\frac{x^n-(-\alpha)^n}{x-(-\alpha)}=\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}(-a)^kx^{n-1-k}
I_n=\int_0^1 \frac{x^n}{x+\alpha}=\int_0^1 \frac{x^n-(-\alpha)^n}{x-(-\alpha)} + \int_0^1 \frac{(-\alpha)^n}{x+\alpha}
I_n=\int_0^1\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}(-\alpha)^kx^{n-1-k}+(-\alpha)^n(\log(1+\alpha)-\log(\alpha))
I_n=\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\int_0^1(-\alpha)^kx^{n-1-k}+(-\alpha)^n\log(\frac{1+\alpha}{\alpha})
I_n=\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\frac{(-\alpha)^k}{n-k}+(-\alpha)^n\log\left(\frac{1+\alpha}{\alpha}\right)
